THE GAME
--------

  'Krystal_Kaves' is a Workbench game where you try to find
coloured crystals that are randomly placed here and there in a
labyrinth of caverns where the walls are formed by white crystals.
When you have found a number of crystals, go to the exit of the
area...

  4 types of crystals can be found, one type of crystal has a high
value, while the other types of crystals are more plentiful but of
a much lower value...

  Have fun!

FEATURES
--------

-Simple installation: just run the game and play!

-The game can be played by using the mouse or the cursor keys of
 the keyboard.

-A game you can play while waiting for other tasks to complete...
 or just for fun!

-Small package, the Lha archive is smaller than 50 kilobytes, so
 it doesn't take ages to download ...although, you can play
 another of my Workbench games while downloading this game ;)

-The game plays on the Workbench screen and its window is
 resizeable.

